  "description": "<i>RISK: The Game of Global Domination</i> is a conversion of the classic board game <i>Risk</i>. Your aim is to wipe out your opponents and conquer the world by placing your armies and attacking neighbouring territories. The CD-ROM version of the game features an exact conversion of the Classic board game against human or AI opponents, as well as Ultimate Risk, a more complex game where a completely new strategy is needed, involving Generals, forts and different terrain types.<br><br>Other features include new maps, the challenging Blind Risk, fully animated battle scenes and a second CD to allow easy network gaming.",
